name: CHUCK RAGAN AT THE BONEYARD, NJ
description:
Hand screen printed for Chuck Ragan's sold out solo show at the Boneyard in Atlantic City, NJ on November 3rd 2013. The show was for 1787 Collective's 2 year anniversary. Jared Hart of The Scandals and Westgate also played. This is what is left of the 75 that were printed. Signed and numbered for the show. Printed by Clawhammer Studios.

• 12.5"x19" 
• 1 color (blood) on True White French Speckltone Paper
• Limited to 75 
• Signed & Numbered

name: HOT WATER MUSIC AT THE GRAMERCY THEATER, NYC
description:
Hand screened print for Hot Water Music's two sold out shows in NYC at the Gramercy Theater. The first show on 5.21.12 was with Iron Chic and Daytrader and the second on 5.22.12 was with The Menzingers and Luther.

• 12.5"x19"
• 2 colors (electric red/dead sea blue) on French Construction Paper (grout grey)
• 2nd Edition of 50
• Signed & Numbered

name: TED LEO & THE PHARMACISTS AT THE BELL HOUSE
description:
This is a joint print for Ted Leo & the Pharmacists two shows on 12.30.11 at The Bell House (Brooklyn, NY) with Obits & Kurt Braunohler and Maxwell's (Hoboken, NJ) on 12.31.11 with Sharon Van Etten & Kurt Braunohler.

• 12.5" X 19"
• 2 color (teal / dark blue) screen print on archival French Construction  (whitewash) stock
• Edition of 100
• Signed and numbered
